Package com.w10.risk_game.models.strategies

Class AggressivePlayerStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w10.risk_game.models.strategies.PlayerStrategy
      • com.w10.risk_game.models.strategies.AggressivePlayerStrategy
  • public class AggressivePlayerStrategy
extends PlayerStrategy
    The AggressivePlayerStrategy class represents a strategy for a player in a game, where the player deploys armies on their strongest country, attacks neighboring countries with their strongest country, and moves armies to maximize force.
    Author:
    Darlene-Naz

      • getNeighborsWithEnemies

        private List<Country> getNeighborsWithEnemies​(Country p_fromCountry)
        The function returns a list of neighboring countries of a given country that have at least one enemy neighbor, sorted by their army count in descending order.
        Parameters:
        p_fromCountry - The parameter "p_fromCountry" represents the country for which we want to find its neighboring countries that have enemies.
        Returns:
        The method is returning a list of countries that are neighbors of the given "p_fromCountry" and have at least one neighbor that is owned by a different player. The list is sorted in descending order based on the number of armies in each country.
